    <span class="slide-number">1 / 12</span>
    <div class="hero-badge">Series A Round</div>
    <h1><span class="gradient-text">AUTONOVA</span><br>AI Infrastructure for Southeast Asia</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Building the unified edge platform for the next billion AI applications</p>
    <div class="ask-amount">Raising $15M</div>
  </section>

  <!-- Slide 2: Problem -->
  <section class="slide" data-slide="2" data-title="Problem">
    <span class="slide-number">2 / 12</span>
    <h2>The Problem</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">Legacy cloud infrastructure is failing modern AI workloads in Southeast Asia</p>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🔌</div>
        <h4>Fragmented APIs</h4>
        <p>Developers juggle 5+ vendors to deploy a single AI model. No unified interface, conflicting SDKs, and weeks of integration work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">💸</div>
        <h4>High Costs</h4>
        <p>AWS/Azure pricing in USD crushes SEA startups. 60-80% margin erosion from egress fees and idle compute charges.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">⏱️</div>
        <h4>Latency Issues</h4>
        <p>300-500ms round trips to US-West datacenters kill real-time AI. Users abandon apps over 200ms delays.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Slide 3: Solution -->
  <section class="slide" data-slide="3" data-title="Solution">
    <span class="slide-number">3 / 12</span>
    <h2>Our Solution</h2>
    <p class="subtitle">One platform. Edge-native. Built for AI-first companies in Southeast Asia.</p>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
        <h4>Unified API Gateway</h4>
        <p>Single endpoint for LLMs, embeddings, vector DBs, and inference. OpenAI-compatible. Switch providers in 1 line of code.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
        <h4>Edge Computing</h4>
        <p>14 edge nodes across SEA. 95th percentile latency under 50ms. Models run closer to your users, not in Virginia.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">📈</div>
        <h4>Auto-scaling</h4>
        <p>From 0 to 10K RPS in 30s. Pay only for compute used. Zero idle costs. GPU pooling cuts inference costs by 70%.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

